# Input

```scss
@supports foo(bar: baz) {
  .a { color: red; }
}

@supports (foo(bar: baz)) and (display: grid) {
  .b { display: grid; }
}

@supports foo(url("a.svg" namespace.fn(test))) {
  .c { color: green; }
}

```


# Formatted

```scss
@supports foo(bar: baz) {
	.a {
		color: red;
	}
}

@supports (foo(bar: baz)) and (display: grid) {
	.b {
		display: grid;
	}
}

@supports foo(url("a.svg"namespace.fn(test))) {
	.c {
		color: green;
	}
}

```
